desc_long								关于这款游戏							Tower Unite is a living, evolving world, fueled by the community. Play online games with your friends or make new friends from around the world!Tower Unite is a large online multiplayer game that spans genres.Play minigames such as Minigolf, Ball Race, Virus, and more!Earn itemsHang with your friends in your own personalized houseConnect with others through a massive Plaza with various attractions and gamesParty with friends!Watch synchronized media such as YouTube or SoundcloudSuggest new features - we listen!No microtransactions or subscription feesTower Unite has many games to play, with more to come, such as...Supports up to 16 players online4 courses with 18 holes (72 holes total) and more in the works!Based on the original 2009 minigolf hit from GMod Tower that inspired other gamesHole-in-one fireworksWear tiny hats on your golf ballPutt in snow, japanese gardens, mines, and even in the sky!Simultaneous puttingPlayer hosted serversSupports up to 20 players online5 unique levelsRoll around in a giant ballSpeed past tricky obstaclesPlayer hosted serversSupports up to 12 players onlineFast paced old school first person shooting actionSurvive in 3 unique levelsBlast infected away with 12 sci-fi weaponsTeam tag elimination, with weaponsPlayer hosted serversOnce you've played some of the games, head on over to your personal space...In Tower Unite, everyone has their own personal space, called a Condo.Place tons of different furniture and itemsWatch synchronized media such as YouTubePlace images from the internet directly into the game synced with online playersListen to synchronized music with SoundcloudCustomize wallpapers, lights, and time of dayInvite friends to party, chat, voice chat, drink, and eat virtual pizza!Play instruments like a piano or drumsInteract with various weird and cool itemsBuild unique creationsGet a pet cat or dogCook/craft food and new itemsFrom the Condo, you can exit through your front door into a bigger online experience called the Plaza. The Plaza acts as a gathering point, like a shopping mall.Gamble at the CasinoPlay games at the ArcadeWalk along the Boardwalk and enjoy Bowling, Laser Tag, Bumper Cars, or ride the Ferris Wheel or RollercoasterWatch synchronized YouTube videos in the TheaterShop for new items at different storesConnect to the bigger Game WorldsGo fishing and explore the ocean with your friendsVoice chat and text chatPlayer hosted serversDO MORE THAN OTHER VIRTUAL WORLD GAMESTower Unite isn't just a walk-around-and-chat simulator. You can run, jump, crouch, use jetpacks, get drunk, dance, sit, throw-up, lounge in pool tubes, and much much more.Play multiplayer games of various genres online with friends.Play online Minigolf with up to 16 players.Customize yourself with accessories.Furnish and design the layout of your personal space (the Condo) with furniture and interactive toys.Invite other players over to your Condo for parties and mini-games.Watch synchronized YouTube videos in a virtual theater or your Condo.Fly around in jetpacks.Imbibe alcohol to an irresponsible extent.Join official servers or host your own server.Hang out with your friends or find new friends!Enjoy free DLC, no microtransactions, and developer support.Collect tons of unique items with Steam Inventory support.						
